      "id": "PopularPost298237",
      "post_content": " Play Sturmgeist in standard like a boss, the complete guide.  \n  \nTurn 1: Draw, play a mountain, [Goblin Arsonist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Arsonist),   \nTurn 2: Draw, play a Mountain, [Infernal Plunge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Infernal Plunge), [Goblin Arsonist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Arsonist) again, [Infernal Plunge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Infernal Plunge) once more. Play [Chromatic Lantern](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chromatic Lantern) x2 (you need to tap one to play the other).  \nTurn 3: Draw, play an Island, [Sturmgeist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sturmgeist). Goes to graveyard due to having no cards in hand at this point. Laugh about, it concede, and don't build a deck around trying to get this card out as fast as possible since this really doesn't have a spot outside of control decks that refill their hands frequently.",
      "posted_by": "Rootkit9208",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost298237\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\"> Play Sturmgeist in standard like a boss, the complete guide.<br/><br/>Turn 1: Draw, play a mountain, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Arsonist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Arsonist\">Goblin Arsonist</a>, <br/>Turn 2: Draw, play a Mountain, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Infernal Plunge\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Infernal Plunge\">Infernal Plunge</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Arsonist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Arsonist\">Goblin Arsonist</a> again, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Infernal Plunge\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Infernal Plunge\">Infernal Plunge</a> once more. Play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chromatic Lantern\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chromatic Lantern\">Chromatic Lantern</a> x2 (you need to tap one to play the other).<br/>Turn 3: Draw, play an Island, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sturmgeist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sturmgeist\">Sturmgeist</a>. Goes to graveyard due to having no cards in hand at this point. Laugh about, it concede, and don't build a deck around trying to get this card out as fast as possible since this really doesn't have a spot outside of control decks that refill their hands frequently.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '298237'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Re